OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FPlenty of sunshine Thursday, after a
OL,7,Fgrey start. Perhaps a few more showers
OL,8,Fdeveloping on Friday, otherwise
OL,9,Fstaying warm and sunny. These becoming
OL,10,Fmore numerous come Saturday.
